/l/04/cd/66237_G402G.jpg","common":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/400/pic/cover/l/04/cd/66237_G402G.jpg"},"summary":"      《狐狸与猎狗》是一部由华特迪士尼于1981年制作并发行的动画电影。它的上映日期是1981年7月10日，为第24部华特迪士尼经典动画长片。\r\n       其内容的故事是自1967年所著之同名小说改编而来，同这个故事剧情感人，被网路评为迪士尼最感人的作品。在这部电影中，故事讲述了狐狸陶德（Tod）和猎狗小铜（Copper）的友谊，两个童年时的欢乐时光，两个朋友相对的日子随着时间的推移而慢慢逼近，从好朋友变成敌人的故事。 米基·鲁尼（Mickey Rooney）负责陶德（Tod）的配音，寇特·罗素（Kurt Russel）是小铜（Copper）的配音。","name":"The Fox and the Hound","name_cn":"狐狸与猎狗","tags":[{"name":"Disney","count":13,"total_cont":0},{"name":"剧场版","count":9,"total_cont":0},{"name":"欧美","count":8,"total_cont":0},{"name":"1981","count":8,"total_cont":0},{"name":"迪士尼","count":8,"total_cont":0},{"name":"动画电影","count":6,"total_cont":0},{"name":"童年","count":4,"total_cont":0},{"name":"治愈","count":4,"total_cont":0},{"name":"MickeyRooney","count":2,"total_cont":0},{"name":"RichardRich","count":2,"total_cont":0},{"name":"美国","count":2,"total_cont":0},{"name":"ArtStevens","count":2,"total_cont":0},{"name":"TedBerman","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"电影","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"アニメ映画","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"20世纪","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"小说改","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"美国动画","count":1,"total_cont":0}],"infobox":[{"key":"中文名","value":"狐狸与猎狗"},{"key":"上映年度","value":"1981年7月10日"},{"key":"片长","value":"83 分钟"},{"key":"导演","value":"Art Stevens / Richard Rich / Ted Berman"},{"key":"编剧","value":"Burny Mattinson / Daniel P. Mannix / David Michener"},{"key":"主演","value":"米基·鲁尼 / 库尔特·拉塞尔 / 珀尔·贝利 / 杰克·艾伯森 / Sandy Duncan / 珍妮特·诺兰 / Pat Buttram / 约翰·菲尔德"},{"key":"话数","value":"1"}],"rating":{"rank":0,"total":34,"count":{"1":0,"2":0,"3":0,"4":0,"5":3,"6":10,"7":11,"8":9,"9":0,"10":1},"score":6.9},"total_episodes":0,"collection":{"on_hold":2,"dropped":6,"wish":9,"collect":59,"doing":1},"id":66237,"eps":1,"meta_tags":["剧场版"],"volumes":0,"series":false,"locked":false,"nsfw":false,"type":2},{"date":"1981-07-04","platform":"剧场版","images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/200/pic/cover/l/8f/a7/67755_ZlhnK.jpg","grid":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/cover/l/8f/a7/67755_ZlhnK.jpg","large":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/l/8f/a7/67755_ZlhnK.jpg","medium":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/800/pic/cover/l/8f/a7/67755_ZlhnK.jpg","common":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/400/pic/cover/l/8f/a7/67755_ZlhnK.jpg"},"summary":"前作映画の続編で、前半はテレビシリーズ『あしたのジョー2』の再編集。終盤は放映中だったテレビシリーズに先行して制作・公開され、のちにテレビシリーズに流用されている。また、声優も一部変更されている。\r\n\r\n-\r\n\r\n宿命のライバル・力石徹の死から1年後。ドヤ街の丹下ボクシングジムには行方不明だったはずの矢吹丈の姿があった。再びリングに立つ丈。しかし彼は、力石の死のショックから相手の顔面を殴れないというボクサーとして致命的な心の傷を抱えていた。そんな丈を案じ白木葉子は南米の強豪カーロスとの試合を用意。激闘のなかでトラウマを乗り越えた丈は完全復帰を果たし、世界最強のチャンピオン、ホセ・メンドーサとの戦いに挑んでいく。","name":"あしたのジョー2","name_cn":"剧场版 明日之丈2","tags":[{"name":"剧场版","count":66,"total_cont":0},{"name":"1981","count":40,"total_cont":0},{"name":"出崎统","count":40,"total_cont":0},{"name":"漫画改","count":26,"total_cont":0},{"name":"明日之丈","count":26,"total_cont":0},{"name":"总集篇","count":25,"total_cont":0},{"name":"虫Production","count":16,"total_cont":0},{"name":"热血","count":13,"total_cont":0},{"name":"漫改","count":13,"total_cont":0},{"name":"日本","count":7,"total_cont":0},{"name":"出﨑統","count":6,"total_cont":0},{"name":"虫制作","count":5,"total_cont":0},{"name":"日本动画","count":4,"total_cont":0},{"name":"拳击","count":4,"total_cont":0},{"name":"東京ムービー","count":4,"total_cont":0},{"name":"运动","count":3,"total_cont":0},{"name":"1980s","count":3,"total_cont":0},{"name":"TMS","count":2,"total_cont":0},{"name":"体育","count":2,"total_cont":0},{"name":"电影","count":2,"total_cont":0},{"name":"燃尽的神场景","count":2,"total_cont":0},{"name":"动画","count":2,"total_cont":0},{"name":"映画","count":2,"total_cont":0},{"name":"80年代","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"旧物","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"燃","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"トムス・エンタテインメント","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"-1990","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"大长篇","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"1980-1989","count":1,"total_cont":0}],"infobox":[{"key":"中文名","value":"剧场版 明日之丈2"},{"key":"别名","value":[{"v":"劇場版 あしたのジョー2"}]},{"key":"上映年